{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Welcome to Robo Hunt: Dive into an exhilarating multiplayer experience where three players join forces to battle a formidable boss monster, controlled by a fourth player. This is not your ordinary boss fight\u2014strategize, adapt, and conquer in a dynamic environment where every map brings new twists and mechanics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Key Features:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Asymmetric Multiplayer Combat:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Engage in thrilling 3v1 battles where teamwork and strategy are paramount. Three hunters with unique abilities face off against a powerful player-controlled boss monster.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008310/extras/Roller_Portal.gif?t=1732037050\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Diverse Hunter Classes:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Choose from a variety of hunter classes, each with distinct abilities and playstyles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008310/extras/characters.png?t=1732037050\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Formidable Boss Monsters:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Take on the role of the boss monster and unleash chaos with devastating attacks and unique powers. Each monster offers a different challenge, requiring hunters to adapt their strategies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008310/extras/Foron_ult.gif?t=1732037050\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Dynamic Maps with Unique Mechanics:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore diverse maps, each featuring its own set of twists and mechanics that can turn the tide of battle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=